#: ./advtech/sq_hardlight_fusion_and_gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A custom capacitor component for the hardlight rifle, a modification that "
"compresses and solidifies photons. The densely compressed photon shells "
"explode on impact, scattering shrapnel like a grenade."
msgstr ""

