#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hazardous waste drum'}
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid "A yellow drum meant for the storage of hazardous substances."
msgstr "Бочка желтого цвета, предназначенная для хранения опасных веществ."

#: ./advtech/sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid "graphene sheets"
msgid_plural "graphene sheets"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'graphene sheets', 'str_pl': 'graphene sheets'}
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid ""
"A thin polymeric carbon allotrope in which carbon atoms form a hexagonal "
"structure. Used to make materials with layered carbides."
msgstr ""
"Тонкий полимерный аллотроп углерода, в котором атомы углерода образуют "
"гексагональную структуру. Используется для получения материалов со слоистыми"
" карбидами."

#: ./advtech/sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid "layered carbides"
msgid_plural "layered carbides"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'layered carbides', 'str_pl': 'layered carbides'}
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid ""
"Reinforced layered carbide armor plates, which can be used to craft or "
"repair high-tech equipment made of layered carbide."
msgstr ""
"Усиленные пластины брони из многослойных твердых сплавов, которые могут быть"
" использованы для изготовления или ремонта высокотехнологичного оборудования"
" из многослойного твердого сплава."

#: ./advtech/sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid "vertigon"
msgid_plural "vertigon"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vertigon', 'str_pl': 'vertigon'}
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid ""
"It is an unknown mass of particles that possesses a bizarre property—defying"
" Earth’s gravity and constantly “falling” into the void—and emits a deep, "
"unstable amethyst-like purple glow. Even when simply held in one’s hand, an "
"unpleasant force field seems to pull the palm upward, while a nerve-grating,"
" subtle vibration seeps deep into the bones. This pale mass of particles, "
"which giant corporations regard as the heart of overtechnology, induces a "
"cosmic vertigo severe enough to tear apart a human’s semicircular canals "
"simply by being kept nearby without a shielding barrier. Perhaps these "
"particles possess a will of their own."
msgstr ""

#: ./advtech/sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid "bundles of layered carbides"
msgid_plural "bundles of layered carbides"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bundles of layered carbides', 'str_pl': 'bundles
#. of layered carbides'}
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid ""
"Layered carbides, bundled tightly together for storage.  Activate or "
"disassemble to unpack."
msgstr ""
"Многослойные твердые сплавы, плотно упакованные для хранения.  Для "
"распаковки активируйте или разберите."

#: ./advtech/sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid "nuclear waste"
msgid_plural "nuclear waste"
msgstr[0] "ядерные отходы"
msgstr[1] "ядерных отходов"
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'nuclear waste'}
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid "A small pellet of silvery metal, still warm to the touch."
msgstr "Небольшая крупинка серебристого металла, еще теплого на ощупь."

#: ./advtech/sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid "enriched uranium canisters"
msgid_plural "enriched uranium canisters"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enriched uranium canisters', 'str_pl': 'enriched
#. uranium canisters'}
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid ""
"A container containing enriched uranium that has been solidified by applying"
" pressure to uranium separated from the gas. It is highly radioactive and "
"must be handled with extreme care."
msgstr ""
"Контейнер, содержащий обогащенный уран, затвердевший в результате "
"воздействия давления на уран, выделенный из газа. Он обладает высокой "
"радиоактивностью и требует крайне осторожного обращения."

#: ./advtech/sq_nano_generic_comp.json
msgid "depleted uranium"
msgid_plural "depleted uranium"
msgstr[0] "обеднённый уран"
msgstr[1] "обеднённого урана"
