#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "UPS"
msgid_plural "UPS's"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'UPS', 'str_pl': "UPS's"}
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"This is a unified power supply, or UPS.  It is a civilian evolution of a "
"military project.  Designed to power advanced weapons and armor, the "
"civilian version serves as a portable power bank and inverter for many "
"household electronics.  It can be worn around to either leg for ease of "
"access."
msgstr ""

#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "advanced UPS"
msgid_plural "advanced UPS's"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'advanced UPS', 'str_pl': "advanced UPS's"}
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"This is an advanced version of the unified power supply, or UPS.  This "
"device has been significantly redesigned to provide better efficiency as "
"well as to consume plutonium fuel cells rather than batteries, and is both "
"slimmer and lighter to wear.  Sadly, its plutonium reactor can't be charged "
"in UPS charging station."
msgstr ""

#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "bionic splints"
msgstr "Бионическая шина"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bionic splints'}
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"A bionic splint helps your broken limb heal.  Your broken limb will heal 4x "
"faster."
msgstr ""
"Бионическая шина помогает заживлению сломанной конечности.  Сломанная "
"конечность заживает в 4 раза быстрее."

#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "bionic arm splints"
msgid_plural "bionic arm splintss"
msgstr[0] "бионические шины для рук"
msgstr[1] "бионических шин для рук"
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bionic arm splints'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bionic leg splints'}
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"Advanced splint. Less restrictive on limb movement, and quickly immobilizes "
"broken bones."
msgstr ""
"Усовершенствованная шина. В меньшей степени ограничивает движения "
"конечностей и быстро иммобилизует сломанные кости."

#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "bionic leg splints"
msgid_plural "bionic leg splintss"
msgstr[0] "бионические шины на ногу"
msgstr[1] "бионических шин на ногу"
msgstr[2] ""

#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "binary sword"
msgid_plural "binary swords"
msgstr[0] "Двоичный цифровой меч"
msgstr[1] "Двоичных цифровых мечей"
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'binary sword'}
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"Light and dark.  Black and white.  Life and death.  The Binary Sword holds "
"no middle ground as it turns your opponents OFF. The numbers 100111100 are "
"etched into the blade."
msgstr ""
"Свет и тьма. Черное и белое. Жизнь и Смерть. Двоичному мечу плевать кто-ты "
"ведь всего лишь одного взмаха хватит чтобы обнулить любого. На клинке "
"выведены цифры 100111100 в двоичном коде."

#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "monomolecular wire"
msgid_plural "monomolecular wires"
msgstr[0] "мономолекулярная проволока"
msgstr[1] "мономолекулярных проволок"
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'monomolecular wire'}
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"A slender wire made of twisted monomolecular fibers. It's hard to handle "
"because it's a wire, but it can be easily concealed in a wrist or pocket, "
"making it an ideal assassination weapon."
msgstr ""
"Тонкая проволока из скрученных мономолекулярных волокон. С ним трудно "
"обращаться, поскольку это проволока, но его можно легко спрятать в запястье "
"или кармане, что делает его идеальным оружием для устранения."

#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "carbon jumpsuit"
msgid_plural "carbon jumpsuits"
msgstr[0] "Карбоновый комбинезон"
msgstr[1] "Карбоновых комбинезонов"
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'carbon jumpsuit'}
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"A thin, full-body garment made from layers of graphene sheets that is "
"lightweight, durable, and provides freedom of movement. It's one of the "
"essential pieces of gear for seasoned adventurers."
msgstr ""
"Тонкая одежда для всего тела, изготовленная из слоев графеновых листов, "
"отличается легкостью, прочностью и свободой движений. Это один из основных "
"предметов снаряжения для опытных искателей приключений."

#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "carbon insulation suit"
msgid_plural "carbon insulation suits"
msgstr[0] "Изолированный карбоновый костюм"
msgstr[1] "Изолированный карбоновых костюмов"
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'carbon insulation suit'}
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"A thin, full-body garment made from overlapping sheets of graphene that is "
"lightweight, durable, and provides freedom of movement. It is one of the "
"essential pieces of equipment for seasoned adventurers exploring extreme "
"regions."
msgstr ""
"Тонкая одежда для всего тела, изготовленная из наложенных друг на друга "
"листов графена, отличается легкостью, прочностью и свободой движений. "
"Является одним из основных предметов экипировки для опытных искателей "
"приключений в экстремальных регионах."

#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "carbon full-body suit"
msgid_plural "carbon full-body suits"
msgstr[0] "карбоновый полнотелый костюм"
msgstr[1] "карбоновых полнотелых костюмов"
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'carbon full-body suit'}
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"A thin, full-body garment made from layers of graphene sheets, it's "
"lightweight, durable, and provides freedom of movement. It's one of the "
"essential pieces of gear for seasoned adventurers who don't want to give "
"away their identity."
msgstr ""
"Тонкая одежда, изготовленная из слоев графеновых листов, легка, прочна и "
"обеспечивает свободу движений. Это один из необходимых предметов экипировки "
"для опытных искателей приключений, которые не хотят выдавать свою личность "
"или как то защитить шею с головой."

#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "heat blade"
msgid_plural "heat blades"
msgstr[0] "Тепловое лезвие"
msgstr[1] "Тепловые ножи"
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'heat blade'}.
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "You heat up the blade to bright red."
msgstr ""
"Вы разогреваете лезвие до высоких температур пока не обретет ярко-красного "
"свечение."

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'heat blade'}
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"A metal blade that is energized to generate high heat. This weapon can "
"easily cut through enemies with the sharpness of the blade and the force of "
"the high heat. Use to heat up the weapon."
msgstr ""
"Металлическое лезвие, на которое подается электрический ток, генерирующий "
"высокую температуру. Это оружие использует остроту лезвия и силу тепла, "
"чтобы с легкостью рассекать врагов. Вы почувствуете прилив сил, когда "
"достанете оружие. Используйте его для включения."

#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "heat blade (on)"
msgid_plural "heat blade (on)s"
msgstr[0] "Тепловое лезвие (on)"
msgstr[1] "Тепловых лезвий (on)"
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'heat blade (on)'}.
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "You turned off the heat blade."
msgstr "Вы отключили тепловое лезвие."

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'heat blade (on)'}
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"A metal blade that is electrically charged to generate high heat. This "
"weapon uses the sharpness of the blade and the power of the heat to cut "
"through enemies with ease. You'll feel a thrill of power as you draw the "
"weapon. Use to turn off the weapon."
msgstr ""
"Металлическое лезвие, на которое подается электрический ток, генерирующий "
"высокую температуру. Это оружие использует остроту лезвия и силу тепла, "
"чтобы с легкостью рассекать врагов. Вы почувствуете прилив сил, когда "
"достанете оружие. Используйте его для отключения."

#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "experimental hardlight blade (off)"
msgid_plural "experimental hardlight blade (off)s"
msgstr[0] "Экспериментальное фотонное лезвие (off)"
msgstr[1] "Экспериментальных фотонных лезвий (off)"
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'experimental hardlight blade (off)'}.
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "You turn on the hardlight blade."
msgstr "Вы отключили фотонное лезвие."

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'experimental hardlight blade (off)'}
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"The Rivtech RMX-01 Experimental Hardlight Blade is a powerful weapon "
"utilizing laser technology, an eternal symbol of Jedi warriors, a fiery "
"testament to Newton, and the pinnacle of otaku science.  You can turn it on "
"using."
msgstr ""
"Ривтех© \"RMX-01 Экспериментальное Фотонное Лезвие\" - это мощное оружие, "
"использующее лазерные технологии, вечный символ воинов-джедаев, пламенное "
"свидетельство Ньютона.  Используйте его чтобы включить."

#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "experimental hardlight blades (on)"
msgid_plural "experimental hardlight blades (on)"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'experimental hardlight blades (on)',
#. 'str_pl': 'experimental hardlight blades (on)'}.
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid "You turn off the hardlight blade."
msgstr "Вы отключаете экспериментальное фотонное лезвие."

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'experimental hardlight blades (on)', 'str_pl':
#. 'experimental hardlight blades (on)'}
#: ./advtech/sq_nano_tier.json
msgid ""
"The Rivtech RMX-01 Experimental Hardlight Blade is a powerful weapon "
"utilizing laser technology, an eternal symbol of Jedi warriors, a fiery "
"testament to Newton, and the pinnacle of otaku science.  It can be turned "
"off by using."
msgstr ""
"Ривтех© \"RMX-01 Экспериментальное Фотонное Лезвие\" - это мощное оружие, "
"использующее лазерные технологии, вечный символ воинов-джедаев, пламенное "
"свидетельство Ньютона. Используйте его чтобы выключить."

#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "multi-chamber hydrogen bladder"
msgid_plural "multi-chamber hydrogen bladders"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for multi-chamber hydrogen bladder
#. ~ Description for external multi-chamber hydrogen bladder
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'multi-chamber hydrogen bladder'}
#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"This invention serves as a living demonstration of why airships of the past "
"used helium instead of hydrogen—and why even those helium-filled airships "
"eventually faded into history. Packed a pouch made of graphene sheets to the"
" brim with hydrogen. Thanks to the honeycomb-shaped multi-wall structure, a "
"single peck from a bird won’t cause it to crash immediately, but staying "
"away from incendiary bombs or Molotov cocktails is the best way to preserve "
"both your life and the vehicle’s frame."
msgstr ""

#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "external multi-chamber hydrogen bladder"
msgstr ""

#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "anti-gravity hover systems"
msgid_plural "anti-gravity hover systems"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for anti-gravity hover systems
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'anti-gravity hover systems', 'str_pl': 'anti-
#. gravity hover systems'}
#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"This is a multipurpose anti-gravity thruster that replaces the wheels. It "
"glides effortlessly over swamps and ruins, defying the friction of the "
"earth. Countless corporate test pilots have been crushed against concrete "
"walls after losing control of this merciless hunk of metal."
msgstr ""

#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "anti-gravity levitation module"
msgid_plural "anti-gravity levitation modules"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for anti-gravity levitation module
#. ~ Description for external anti-gravity levitation module
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'anti-gravity levitation module'}
#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"This anti-gravity subsystem utilizes the unstable force field of the "
"vertigon to effectively nullify the physical mass of vehicles weighing "
"several tons. A massive, heavily armored fortress equipped with this module "
"can glide effortlessly over swamps and ruins, as if made of feathers, "
"completely ignoring terrain penalties."
msgstr ""

#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "external anti-gravity levitation module"
msgstr ""

#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "anti-gravity thruster"
msgid_plural "anti-gravity thrusters"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for anti-gravity thruster
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'anti-gravity thruster'}
#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"This is an inhumane propulsion system that generates immense acceleration by"
" channeling vertigon’s unstable repulsive field backward. The moment the "
"ignition switch is pressed, a murderous gravitational acceleration—seemingly"
" strong enough to shatter the backrest—threatens the pilot’s spine. However,"
" corporate accountants simply record the rupture of a pilot’s internal "
"organs as “acceptable operational losses” if this brute-force thrust can "
"break through enemy defenses."
msgstr ""

#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "external anti-gravity thruster"
msgstr ""

#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "vehicle manipulator workbench"
msgstr "Автомобильный верстак с манипулятором"

#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "cargo dimension"
msgstr "cargo dimension"

#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "MetalMaster forge buddy"
msgid_plural "MetalMaster forge buddies"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'MetalMaster forge buddy'}
#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"A welding and metalworking station, powered by the vehicle's battery.  "
"'e'xamine the forge rig to utilize its welder or soldering iron; you'll "
"still need glare protection."
msgstr ""

#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "cooking rig"
msgid_plural "cooking rigs"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cooking rig'}
#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"An all-in-one kitchen unit and chemistry lab.  'e'xamine it to use its "
"hotplate to heat up food or drinks."
msgstr ""

#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "KitchenMaster cooking buddy"
msgid_plural "KitchenMaster cooking buddies"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'KitchenMaster cooking buddy'}
#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"An all-in-one kitchen unit, chemistry lab, and food preparation area.  "
"'e'xamine it to use its hotplate to heat up food or drinks."
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'MetalMaster forge buddy', 'str_pl': 'MetalMaster
#. forge buddies'}
#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"From the makers of the best-selling* FOODCO kitchen buddy comes the "
"MetalMaster forge buddy, for all your metalworking, firing, and welding "
"needs!  It's just as clunky and awkward as the thing it's spinning off, and "
"still requires a vehicle battery to function."
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'KitchenMaster cooking buddy', 'str_pl':
#. 'KitchenMaster cooking buddies'}
#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"Because it *clearly* needed one, this large all-in-one station provides the "
"functions of FOODCO's kitchen buddy, now with complementary fume hoods and "
"chemistry materials.  Why a chef would need a chemical rig is anyone's "
"guess, but you can mount it on a vehicle to make use of it."
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cooking rig'}
#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"Skillet, pot, hotplate, and chemistry set; everything you need to cook food "
"and chemicals.  Includes proper fume vents and a separator, so you don't "
"contaminate your food with toxic chemicals."
msgstr ""

#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "cargo freezers"
msgid_plural "cargo freezers"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cargo freezers', 'str_pl': 'cargo freezers'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cargo freezers'}
#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"A large version of the 300 litre capacity freezer designed as a mobile "
"solution for freezing food. It provides insulation from external elements."
msgstr ""
"Большая версия морозильника емкостью 300 литров, разработанная как мобильное"
" решение для замораживания продуктов. Обеспечивает изоляцию от внешних "
"элементов."

#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "superfast recharging station"
msgid_plural "superfast recharging stations"
msgstr[0] "сверхбыстрая зарядная станция"
msgstr[1] "сверхбыстрых зарядных станций"
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'superfast recharging station'}
#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"This is a state-of-the-art charging station that runs on vehicle power. "
"During operation, it will charge any rechargeable battery (cellular, lead-"
"acid, etc.) inserted into the internal storage compartment with ultra-fast "
"charging technology, much faster than a battery charging station. The unit "
"requires a pre-installed storage compartment to install, and can be switched"
" on and off from the dashboard or electronics controls."
msgstr ""
"Это современная зарядная станция, работающая от энергии автомобиля. Во время"
" работы он будет заряжать любую батарею, вставленную во внутренний отсек "
"хранения, с помощью технологии сверхбыстрой зарядки заряжает гораздо "
"быстрее, чем станция зарядки аккумуляторов. Для установки устройства "
"требуется предварительно установленный отсек для хранения, и его можно "
"включать и выключать с помощью приборной панели или электронного управления."

#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid "atomic engine"
msgid_plural "atomic engines"
msgstr[0] "атомный двигатель"
msgstr[1] "атомных двигателей"
msgstr[2] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'atomic engine'}
#: ./advtech/sq_vehicle_part.json
msgid ""
"A nuclear engine that generates electricity through radioactive decay to "
"provide continuous, reliable power for a vehicle. Thanks to its advanced "
"design, there is no wasted power when multiple are installed in a vehicle."
msgstr ""
"Ядерный двигатель, вырабатывающий электроэнергию за счет радиоактивного "
"распада для обеспечения непрерывного и надежного энергоснабжения автомобиля."
" Благодаря усовершенствованной конструкции, при установке в транспортное "
"средство нескольких таких двигателей не происходит потери энергии."

